{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01EWKtshNsoUmaGEzFy5A3Ci","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Written to `tools/title-loop/docs/9-52aa0c8/feedback.md`. Here's the summary:\n\n**Root cause**: The bilingual suppression fires only when `preAllCaps.length === 1`. This document has four ALL_CAPS lines that pass `passesHardFilters` — `PAPRIKA GYERAN-JJIM` (the Korean romanization), `NA 3 PAPRYKI` (serving size), `SKŁADNIKI` and `WARZYWA` (section headers). With `preAllCaps.length === 4`, the suppression never activates.\n\nWithout suppression, `PAPRIKA GYERAN-JJIM` beats `Faszerowana papryka` decisively because it picks up **+0.18 in bonuses** (ALL_CAPS +0.08 + structural heading +0.10) that the correct mixed-case title cannot match.\n\n**Fix direction**: The guard `preAllCaps.length === 1` is too strict. The right check is positional + semantic: is the ALL_CAPS line immediately below position 0, and does it appear to be a translation of the mixed-case title? The count of other ALL_CAPS section headers elsewhere in the document is irrelevant."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1294,"cache_read_input_tokens":34268,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1294},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"05e663a7-2814-4721-a7b5-7c4e35d15ae3","uuid":"94aa14ed-eb5e-47d4-8c05-36ab4810b486"}
